OL,3,CFour more people on trial after woman
OL,4,Cshot dead on her doorstep
OL,6,FFour more people have gone on trial in
OL,7,Fconnection with the murder of a woman
OL,8,Fshot dead on her doorstep in south
OL,9,FWales.
OL,11,FJoanne Penney, 40, died in Talbot
OL,12,FGreen, Rhondda Cynon Taf, last March
OL,13,Fafter suffering a single gunshot wound
OL,14,Fto the chest.
OL,16,FIn January, four people were found
OL,17,Fguilty of murder. Joshua Gordon,
OL,18,FKristina Ginova and Melissa Quailey-
OL,19,FDashper, all from Leicester and Jordan
OL,20,FMills-Smith, from Cardiff, will be
OL,21,Fsentenced later this year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
