OL,3,CFour more people on trial after woman
OL,4,Cshot dead on her doorstep
OL,6,FA fifth defendant, Marcus Huntley,
OL,7,Ffrom Cardiff, previously pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to murder and will also be
OL,9,Fsentenced at a later date.
OL,11,FTony Porter, from Leicester, was found
OL,12,Fnot guilty of murder but was convicted
OL,13,Fof participating in the activities of
OL,14,Fan organised crime group. He was
OL,15,Fsentenced to 22 months in jail.
OL,17,FOn Monday 30 March, four other
OL,18,Fdefendants appeared in the dock at the
OL,19,Fstart of a second trial related to Ms
OL,20,FPenney's death.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
