OL,3,CFour more people on trial after woman
OL,4,Cshot dead on her doorstep
OL,6,FRenaldo Baptiste, formerly of
OL,7,FLeicester, denies murder.
OL,9,FMolly Ruth Cooper, also from
OL,10,FLeicester, is accused of possessing,
OL,11,Fpurchasing or acquiring ammunition
OL,12,Fwithout holding a firearm certificate
OL,13,F- which she denies.
OL,15,FThe court indictment says the charge
OL,16,Frelates to "16 live 8mm calibre blank
OL,17,Fpistol cartridges modified by being
OL,18,Freloaded with improvised projectiles".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
