OL,3,CFour more people on trial after woman
OL,4,Cshot dead on her doorstep
OL,6,FAfter being rearranged, both Baptiste
OL,7,Fand Cooper pleaded guilty to
OL,8,Fparticipating in the activities of an
OL,9,Forganised crime group.
OL,11,FLaura John and Donna James, both from
OL,12,FCardiff, deny a single charge of
OL,13,Fassisting an offender, specifically by
OL,14,Fbuying a coach ticket for Mills-Smith.
OL,16,FThe indictment alleges they did this
OL,17,F"with intent to impede (his)
OL,18,Fapprehension or prosecution".
