OL,3,CFour more people on trial after woman
OL,4,Cshot dead on her doorstep
OL,6,FTwo other men, Sai Raj Ritekh Manne
OL,7,Fand Callum Kelleher, have pleaded
OL,8,Fguilty to participating in the
OL,9,Factivities of an organised crime group
OL,10,Fand will be sentenced in May.
OL,12,FJoanne Penney was shot on the doorstep
OL,13,Fof 10 Llys Illtyd on 9 March 2025 at
OL,14,Faround 6pm after answering a knock at
OL,15,Fthe door.
OL,17,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,18,Fscene, including armed police and
OL,19,Fparamedics, but Ms Penney had
OL,20,Fsustained a fatal shot to the heart.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
